#. html
#: /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/data_quality.env_cloud.xml:128 /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/data_quality.env_cloud.xml:226 /Users/alalji/Downloads/splunk/etc/apps/splunk-monitoring-console/default/data/ui/views/data_quality.xml:159
msgid ""
"<p>This table shows errors and warnings emitted when the index-time settings in place do not allow for the\n"
"          proper processing of ingested data. Issues in this table indicate the presence of one or more of these scenarios:\n"
"        </p><ul><li>\n"
"            Line Breaking Issues -  Lines in the event are too long and exceed the TRUNCATE setting in props.conf.\n"
"            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.linebreak\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn More.</a>\n"
"          </li><li>\n"
"            Timestamp Parsing Issues - The extraction of event time stamps was partially or completely unsuccessful.\n"
"            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.timestamp\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn More.</a>\n"
"          </li><li>\n"
"            Aggregation Issues - The number of lines per event exceeds the MAX_EVENTS setting in props.conf.\n"
"            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.aggregation\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn More.</a>\n"
"          </li><li>\n"
"            Metric Schema Issues - The conversion of log events to metric data was partially or completely unsuccessful.\n"
"            <a href=\"/help?location=settings.sourcetype.logtometrics\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn More.</a>\n"
"          </li><li>\n"
"            Metrics Issues - The collection of metric data was partially or completely unsuccessful.\n"
"            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.metrics\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">Learn More.</a>\n"
"          </li></ul>"
msgstr ""
"<p>이 테이블에는 인덱스 시간 설정이 적용되지 않아 수집된 데이터가 적절히 처리되지 않을 경우 발생하는          오류 및 경고가 표시됩니다. 이 테이블의 문제는 다음 시나리오 중 하나 이상에 해당됨을 나타냅니다.        </p><ul><li>            줄 바꿈 문제 - 이벤트의 줄이 너무 길고 props.conf의 TRUNCATE 설정을 초과합니다.            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.linebreak\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">자세히 알아보기</a>          </li><li>            타임스탬프 파싱 문제 - 이벤트 타임스탬프 추출이 부분적으로 또는 완전히 실패했습니다.              <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.timestamp\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">자세히 알아보기</a>          </li><li>            집계 문제-이벤트당 줄 수가 props.conf의 MAX_EVENTS 설정을 초과합니다.            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.aggregation\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">자세히 알아보기</a>          </li><li>            메트릭 스키마 문제 - 로그 이벤트를 메트릭 데이터로 변환하는 데 부분적으로 또는 완전히 실패했습니다.            <a href=\"/help?location=settings.sourcetype.logtometrics\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">자세히 알아보기</a>          </li><li>            메트릭 문제-메트릭 데이"
"터 수집이 부분적으로 또는 완전히 실패했습니다.            <a href=\"/help?location=learnmore.monitoringconsole.dataquality.metrics\" class=\"external\" target=\"_blank\">자세히 알아보기</a>          </li></ul>"

